{"tid":454914,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【2017秋季日劇】《戀在香港 戀する香港》","createTime":"2017-11-01T15:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T15:55:59.000Z","uid":6640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"461b6312186c5a3915efec46cf0a9f809d421ae5","tid":454914,"uid":6640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:08:44.000Z","msg":"《戀愛香港》是一部懸疑愛情劇，故事環繞五名來歷不同的男女來發展，其中小池榮子飾演女主角真樹，她來到香港，希望跟交友網站上認識的男子見面，卻遇上來港拍紀錄節目的導演吉澤亮。而劇集總共有4集，將於10月初在日本首播。<br />\n<br />\n主演: 小池榮子 / 吉澤亮 / 馬場富美加 / 最上摩卡 / 柳下大<br />\n官方網站: <a href=\"http://www.mbs.jp/koisuru-hongkong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mbs.jp%2Fkoisuru-hongkong%2F&d=sGH9C0NDuTfP17pJWNnFV%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=2b4c7ff8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mbs.jp/koisuru-hongkong/</a><br />\n製片國家/地區: 日本<br />\n首播: 2017-10-10(日本)<br />\n集數: 4<br />\n<br />\n日本仔拍香港都靚過班tvb <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://maplestage.com/episode/zyN9z/%E6%88%80%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%AC%AC1%E9%9B%86-JP171008-Ep-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmaplestage.com%2Fepisode%2FzyN9z%2F%25E6%2588%2580%25E5%259C%25A8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E7%25AC%25AC1%25E9%259B%2586-JP171008-Ep-1&d=sGH9C0NDuTfP17pJWNnFV%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0ebb95d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://maplestage.com/episode/zyN9z/%E6%88%80%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%AC%AC1%E9%9B%86-JP171008-Ep-1</a>"},{"pid":"c614257a078edfad476cf884dffea37999855380","tid":454914,"uid":6640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:10:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://thisdramas.com/5374-22/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthisdramas.com%2F5374-22%2F&d=sGH9C0NDuTfP17pJWNnFV%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=28fc685f\" target=\"_blank\">http://thisdramas.com/5374-22/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個好似好啲"},{"pid":"06442b9f3e006b41da45e2a790ebc168a9d86dad","tid":454914,"uid":6640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11